#hawkular-metrics

## 配置ansible hosts
```

...
#metrics

openshift_hosted_metrics_deploy=true
openshift_hosted_metrics_deployer_prefix=<REGISTRY_IP>:5000/metrics/origin-
openshift_hosted_metrics_deployer_version=v3.6.0
...

```

## 执行命令
```
ansible-playbook -i hosts openshift-ansible/playbooks/byo/openshift-cluster/openshift-metrics.yml

```

## 检查容器状态
```
oc get pod -n openshift-infra
```